name: 8 1/2 x 11 - Glossy Paper HQ Print
description:
Below I have provided a link for a Flickr set that includes all photos available to be ordered as a 8 1/2 x 11 print on HQ glossy paper. If there are any images of mine you've seen posted that you are interested in and do not see them in that set. Please contact me: StefanieMurphyMedia@gmail.com

http://www.flickr.com/photos/67422446@N03/sets/72157631920452922/

Click on full size image you wish to order on flickr and include the link in your note when you checkout so I know which image to send you. Please also include contact information.
